title: Duvnas Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Swedish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Duvnäs Deli is a small take away that offers home-style food made onsite. On the menu is a health plate (quinoa & beans), lentil soup, and vegan burger plus several vegetarian items. Dishes change depending on the day. For dessert, you could order a raw vegan brownie made from coconut oil, dried fruit, nuts and cocoa.
